{
  "stem": "22979.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were fighting for our lives every minute, every minute, either at distribution of the food or getting in a commando where you have a little bit easier.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, like I got-- I didn't fight on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I  was assigned to it, maybe because I looked like maybe 14 years old-- maybe less.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for everything you had to fight-- for your life, for a place to lie down in the evening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got later, you know, the blankets, everybody stole it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know how everybody pushed when you have 10-- 1 blanket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The food, the work, the extreme weather, if-- I tell you something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then later, the selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what it meant coming from work, staying in line, and selection when-- not only on the ramps when they came, but new arrivals came.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They needed room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People, you know, who didn't look so good, who already failed on their health, they couldn't stand straight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or you had marks, you know, bruises around your-- everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to undress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, the SS from the rows-- people-- I mean, girls-- who were in camp already a year, six months-- worn out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they just came out [NON-ENGLISH] from-- from-- from the rows, and separate, and to-- and they were gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a special block in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It called the block 25.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the selection were-- daily.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they had to have at least 1,000 or more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was a [NON-ENGLISH] block, you know, where they concentrated those poor, dying, exhausted, unfortunate in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then at night, or even in the day, trucks came and took them straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But this was later on, because the first gassing was-- you know when-- I forgot to mention there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
